text: Jung Yu-mi (born January 18, 1983) is a South Korean actress. She was born in Busan. She is known for her roles in Family Ties (2006), Chaw (2009), My Dear Desperado (2010), and the box office hits The Crucible (2011) and Train to Busan (2016). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean movie actors Category:Actors from Busan
title: Jung Yu-mi
